column1: # Supplementary Table 2. Genomic position and predicted secondary structure of transcription termination sites (TTS) identified by SEnd-seq. TTS sites were annotated based on E. coli genome NC_000913.3. The sequence from 45-nt upstream to 9-nt downstream of an identified TTS was used for RNA secondary structure prediction with RNAfold combined with custom perl scripts. The characteristics of each TTS are provided.
